sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Operator
  participant Nexus as Archive-Nexus
  participant Ledger as Archive-Ledger
  participant OS as ArchiveOS

  Operator->>Nexus: Generate synthetic cost / settlement event
  Nexus->>Nexus: Store event in Nexus Outbox
  Nexus->>Nexus: Resolve target_service = LEDGER
  Nexus->>Ledger: Publish direct Ledger event
  Ledger->>Ledger: Validate idempotency
  Ledger->>Ledger: Normalize finance_transaction
  Ledger->>Ledger: Generate debit / credit ledger_entry
  Ledger->>Ledger: Run settlement / reconciliation
  OS->>Nexus: Poll outbox summary
  OS->>Ledger: Poll transactions and reconciliation summary
  OS->>OS: Update Control Tower status

